cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper addresses the problem of video captioning using object interactions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed model also involves learning and generating captions, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the model is evaluated on the ActivityNet Captions dataset, which is a multimedia dataset (cs.MM).
